videos.description: Christian Kirk had so much fun returning one punt return for the touchdown earlier in the game that he decided to do it again, this time from 71 yards to increase Texas A&M's lead to 38-3.
videos.headline: Kirk makes it two punt return TDs in one game

videos.description: Christian Kirk returns two punts for touchdowns and adds a third score on a reception to help No. 9 Texas A&M rout New Mexico State 52-10.
videos.headline: Kirk returns 2 punts for TDs, No. 9 Texas A&M rolls

videos.description: Nick Fitzgerald ties a Mississippi State record with seven total touchdowns to lead the Bulldogs to a 56-41 win over Samford.
videos.headline: Fitzgerald has 7 TDs in Mississippi State's 56-41 win
